snippet.title: Togges - Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Togges is a collect-a-thon 3D Platformer about spreading and stacking adorable cubes around the cosmos. Explore multiple worlds and immerse yourself in incredible settings with stunning vistas. From a futuristic city in the Savannah, to a realm made of carrot cake, discover funny stories and make friends around the Cosmos.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
